608DBF14.Line11.BAE4: Through the Day, I have prepared to accept the burden of knowledge.

65381056.Line13.BAE4: Unto Evening, I shall keep it safe, and into the Night hereafter.

E6F0DE2B.Line9.BAE4: From Morning, my eyes were opened, and I saw the coming darkness.
